{
    "title": "HTML Input Form Attributes",
    "content": [
        {
            "heading": "HTML Input Form Attributes",
            "paragraphs": [
                "This chapter describes the attributes for the HTML <input> element."
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The form Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The input form attribute specifies the form the <input> element belongs to. The value must match the id of the <form> element.",
                "Example:\n<form action=\"/action_page.php\" id=\"form1\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n</form>\n<label for=\"lname\">Last name:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"lname\" name=\"lname\" form=\"form1\">"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\" id=\"form1\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n</form>\n<label for=\"lname\">Last name:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"lname\" name=\"lname\" form=\"form1\">"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The formaction Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The formaction attribute specifies the URL of the file that will process the input when the form is submitted, overriding the <form> element's action."
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formaction=\"/action_page2.php\" value=\"Submit as Admin\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The formenctype Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The formenctype attribute specifies how the form-data should be encoded when submitted (for method=\"post\"). It overrides the <form> element's enctype."
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page_binary.asp\" method=\"post\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formenctype=\"multipart/form-data\" value=\"Submit as Multipart/form-data\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The formmethod Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The formmethod attribute defines the HTTP method for sending form-data to the action URL, overriding the <form> element's method.",
                "Example:\n<form action=\"/action_page.php\" method=\"get\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit using GET\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formmethod=\"post\" value=\"Submit using POST\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\" method=\"get\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit using GET\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formmethod=\"post\" value=\"Submit using POST\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The formtarget Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The formtarget attribute specifies where to display the response after submitting the form, overriding the <form> element's target.",
                "Example:\n<form action=\"/action_page.php\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formtarget=\"_blank\" value=\"Submit to a new window/tab\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\">\n    <label for=\"fname\">First name:</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"fname\" name=\"fname\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formtarget=\"_blank\" value=\"Submit to a new window/tab\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The formnovalidate Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The formnovalidate attribute specifies that an <input> element should not be validated when submitted, overriding the <form> element's novalidate.",
                "Example:\n<form action=\"/action_page.php\">\n    <label for=\"email\">Enter your email:</label>\n    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formnovalidate=\"formnovalidate\" value=\"Submit without validation\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\">\n    <label for=\"email\">Enter your email:</label>\n    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n    <input type=\"submit\" formnovalidate=\"formnovalidate\" value=\"Submit without validation\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "The novalidate Attribute",
            "paragraphs": [
                "The novalidate attribute on a <form> specifies that the form-data should not be validated when submitted.",
                "Example:\n<form action=\"/action_page.php\" novalidate>\n    <label for=\"email\">Enter your email:</label>\n    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n</form>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "Example",
            "paragraphs": [
                "<form action=\"/action_page.php\" novalidate>\n    <label for=\"email\">Enter your email:</label>\n    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\"><br>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">\n</form>"
            ]
        }
    ]
}